\end_inset

 is 
\begin_inset Formula $C^{1}$
\end_inset

 at where 
\begin_inset Formula $q\vp^{u}$
\end_inset

 has a unique equilibrium state.
 In particular, we know 
\begin_inset Formula $q\mapsto P(q\vp^{u})$
\end_inset

 for 
\begin_inset Formula $q<1$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

